<div id="content">
	<h1>Departments and Centres</h1>
<p>The BHF CRE in Oxford brings together 36 research groups drawn from 10 different Departments and Centres within the <a href="http://www.medsci.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Medical Sciences Division</a> (MSD) and the <a href="http://www.mpls.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Mathematical, Physical and Life Sciences Division</a> (MPLS) of the University.</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ctsu.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Clinical Trials Service Unit</a>, <a href="http://www.ndm.ox.ac.uk/home" target="_blank">Nuffield Department of Medicine</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cardiov.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Division of Cardiovascular Medicine</a>, <a href="http://www.rdm.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Radcliffe Department of Medicine</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.chem.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Department of Chemistry</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cs.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Department of Computer Science</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.pharm.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Department of Pharmacology</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.dpag.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Department of Physiology, Anatomy and Genetics</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.path.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Sir William Dunn School of Pathology</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.tdi.ox.ac.uk/home" target="_blank">Target Discovery Institute</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.imm.ox.ac.uk/" target="_blank">Weatherall Institute of Molecular Medicine</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.well.ox.ac.uk/home" target="_blank">Wellcome Trust Centre for Human Genetics</a></li>
</ul></div>
